   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-accepting" image="QN_Guard_Steave.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-accepting-acceptted" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Mayor Harold$<BR>If she escaped from Catacomb, she must be home by now…!<BR>Could something have happened to her on her way back?<BR>I'm sorry but could you ask <FONT color=#a82424>Vigilante Guard Steve</FONT> whether he has heard any news?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Mayor Harold$<BR>Thank you. Please find Rose for us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-1" image="QN_Elder_Harold.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(An exotic looking spirit is staring quietly )<BR>(※You have to finish talking to Prairie Town's Mayor Harold)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-1-a" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you know anything about what happened to Rose?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Guard Steve$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. I heard that you're helping out with finding Rose.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-1-a" image="QW_4.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-1-b" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What is going on there?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Guard Steve$<BR>I'm sorry, but there's no news yet. But I received a report that the monsters are acting strangely at <FONT color=#a82424>Shadow Forest Core</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-2" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then I'll go there.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Guard Steve$<BR>Many monsters are said to be gathering at that place.<BR>They seem to be looking for something. Maybe they are looking for Rose?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-2" image="QW_4.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Guard Steve$<BR>I'll pray that you can find Rose at <FONT color=#a82424>Shadow Forest Core</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-a" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Goodbye?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>I can hear the voices of many spirits here.<BR>Do you know, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>? The souls of many nameless soldiers who fought against the Dragon Followers lay asleep here.<BR>It's a good place to say goodbye to you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-b" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Please don't go. I still have many things that I don't know.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>A dead person can't stay in this world for too long. I'm just a handful of spirit energy with the name of Gaharam. I can't maintain this appearance anymore.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-c" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What is that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>I've already passed you all the knowledge that you need.<BR>Except for one.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-d" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You mean I have the Ancient's blood?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>You must have always wondered what that sign on your body is.<BR>That is a proof that you have the Ancient's blood flowing in you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-e" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Shadow Star?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>You are the <FONT color=#a94407>Shadow Star</FONT> of the Prophet. You and her are like light and shadow. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-f" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>W-What do you mean?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>
If the Prophet is taking the good path, you have to hide your existence in her light. If the Prophet is taking the evil path, you have to stop her powers from being misused.<BR>You are the only one who can do this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-g" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>… then because of me, our tribe….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>It must be hard for you to accept it, but you must. <BR>It was our tribe's mission to protect you. Whatever path you took, we were the ones who had to follow you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-2-h" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>… It's hard for me to accept it. But if it's your will….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>Our tribe didn't get killed because of you. Don't blame yourself.<BR>Please accept it even if it's hard. This is the last thing we ask from you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n562_gaharam-3" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>Good girl, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR>Continue to follow the Prophet and observe her. That's your fate.<BR>…Now my heart seems a little lighter.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Gaharam's Spirit smiles comfortably)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n562_gaharam-3" image="QW_PrairieTown.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam's Spirit$<BR>Go back to <FONT color=#a82424>Prairie Town</FONT>.<BR>A new death will strengthen the fate between you and her.<BR>If at any chance… you can't find the path that you're supposed to take, look at <FONT color=#a94407>Hermit's Totem</FONT> and meditate.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-3-a" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You reply no)</html>]]></talk_answer>
