      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-4" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Mayor Harold$<BR>*Sob* Our Rose…What could have happened to her?<BR>I'm sorry but could you ask Vigilante Guard Steve if he has heard any news?</html>]]></talk_question>
